      <property name="text">
       <string>Welcome to The Quest of No Return.

Your mission is to survive the ancient Egyptian temple and reach the sacred Ankh before time runs out.

MOVEMENT
• Use WASD keys to move through the temple.
• Explore carefully and search every chamber.

RIDDLES
• Some rooms contain riddles and ancient puzzles.
• Solve them correctly to continue deeper into the temple.

GUARDIANS
• Dangerous guardians protect the sacred chambers.
• Some guardians chase you while others test your knowledge.

ARTEFACTS
• Collect ancient artefacts hidden across the temple.
• Artefacts may improve score or aid survival.

LIVES &amp; TIMER
• Mistakes may cost lives.
• If all lives are lost or the timer reaches zero, the expedition fails.

GOAL
• Reach the final chamber and claim the sacred Ankh to win.</string>
